EASTERN CARIBBEAN SEA.
GUADELOUPE TO SAINT BARTHELEMY.
NINE METER S/V FAN, WHITE HULL, TWO PERSONS ON BOARD,
OVERDUE LES SAINTES (15-51N 061-36W) TO SAINT BARTHELEMY
(17-54N 062-50W). VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED TO
